title: Hallmark-Stranded in Paradise [2014]
description:
Hallmark-Stranded in Paradise (2014)

Air Date: 9 Aug 2014

Summary: When a driven HR exec loses her high-powered job, she travels to Puerto Rico in an attempt to save her career at a business conference. But as the trip quickly becomes a disaster and a hurricane shuts down the whole island, she meets a handsome world traveler who gives her a new perspective on finding passion in life-and love.
